9:06:42+00:00", "date_published": "2026-05-24T07:06:59+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/levilamina/install-server/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/levilamina/install-server/", "title": "\u5728\u670d\u52a1\u5668\u4e0a\u5b89\u88c5", "content_html": "<h1>\u5728\u670d\u52a1\u5668\u4e0a\u5b89\u88c5</h1>\n<h2>\u524d\u63d0\u6761\u4ef6</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Windows 10\u3001Windows 11\u3001Windows Server 2019\u6216Windows Server 2022\u3002</li>\n<li>[Visual C++ Redistributable for Visual Studio 2015\u30012017\u30012019\u548c2022](htt...</li>\n</ul>", "image": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/translations/levilamina/install-server.png", "date_modified": "2026-05-24T09:06:42+00:00", "date_published": "2026-05-24T07:06:59+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/levilamina/repository-readme/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/levilamina/repository-readme/", "title": "\u4ed3\u5e93README", "content_html": "<h1>\u4ed3\u5e93README</h1>\n<p>/// info | \u6765\u6e90\u4fe1\u606f\n- \u539f\u6587\u4ed3\u5e93\uff1a<a href=\"https://github.com/LiteLDev/LeviLamina\"><code>LiteLDev/LeviLamina</code></a>\n- \u5bf9\u5e94\u6765\u6e90\uff1a<code>.knowledge\\LeviLamina\u6e90\u7801\u53ca\u6587\u6863\\README.zh.md</code>\n///</p>\n<p>![Le...</p>", "image": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/translations/levilamina/repository-readme.png", "date_modified": "2026-05-24T09:06:42+00:00", "date_published": "2026-05-24T09:06:42+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/client/levilamina-client/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/client/levilamina-client/", "title": "LeviLamina\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef\u6a21\u7ec4", "content_html": "<h1>LeviLamina\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef\u6a21\u7ec4</h1>\n<p><strong>LeviLamina\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef\u6a21\u7ec4\uff08LeviLamina Client Mod\uff09</strong>\u662fLeviLamina\u9762\u5411Windows\u7248Minecraft\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef\u7684\u539f\u751f\u6a21\u7ec4\u5f62\u6001\u3002\u5b83\u901a\u8fc7PreLoader\u52a0\u8f7d\u5230\u53d7\u652f\u6301\u7684<code>Minecraft.Windows.exe</code>\u8fdb\u7a0b\uff0c\u5e76\u5728\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef\u6784\u5efa\u4e2d\u63d0\u4f9b...</p>", "image": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/docs/client/levilamina-client.png", "date_modified": "2026-05-24T08:47:19+00:00", "date_published": "2026-05-24T05:44:16+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/server/levilamina/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/server/levilamina/", "title": "LeviLamina", "content_html": "<h1>LeviLamina</h1>\n<p><strong>LeviLamina</strong>\u662f\u9762\u5411Minecraft\u57fa\u5ca9\u7248\u7684\u7b2c\u4e09\u65b9\u6a21\u7ec4\u52a0\u8f7d\u5668\u3002\u5b83\u4ee5<strong>\u57fa\u5ca9\u7248\u4e13\u7528\u670d\u52a1\u5668\uff08Bedrock Dedicated Server\uff09</strong>\uff0c\u901a\u79f0BDS\uff0c\u4e3a\u4e3b\u8981\u8fd0\u884c\u57fa\u7840\uff0c\u901a\u8fc7\u9884\u52a0\u8f7d\u3001\u94a9\u5b50\u548c\u516c\u5171API\u4e3aC++\u6a21\u7ec4\u63d0\u4f9b\u547d\u4ee4\u3001\u4e8b\u4ef6\u3001\u8868\u5355\u3001\u670d\u52a1\u8bbf\u95ee\u3001\u914d\u7f6e\u3001\u6570\u636e\u5b58\u50a8\u3001\u65e5\u5fd7\u548c\u5e95\u5c42...</p>", "image": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/docs/server/levilamina.png", "date_modified": "2026-05-24T08:47:19+00:00", "date_published": "2026-05-23T15:16:46+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/servers/levilamina/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/servers/levilamina/", "title": "LeviLamina\u5165\u95e8", "content_html": "<h1>LeviLamina\u5165\u95e8</h1>\n<p>LeviLamina\u662f\u56f4\u7ed5BDS\u8fd0\u884c\u7684\u7b2c\u4e09\u65b9\u6a21\u7e